## Course Data Files

Download the data files used in the labs and assignments.

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| [stock_returns.xlsx](data/stock_returns.xlsx) | Daily stock returns for AAPL, MSFT, GOOGL, AMZN, META (2023) |
| [factors.xlsx](data/factors.xlsx) | Fama-French factor data (Mkt-RF, SMB, HML, RMW, CMA, RF) |

### Usage Notes

- **stock_returns.xlsx**: Contains daily returns for 5 major tech stocks over 252 trading days
- **factors.xlsx**: Contains Fama-French 5 factors plus the risk-free rate
